; Coverage test for xact.cc line 1050: auto xact amount_expr returning long
; When an automated transaction posting has an expression like (1 * 2)
; that evaluates to a long integer, line 1050 converts it via to_amount().
; The result is then multiplied by the initial post amount at line 1062.

= /^Expenses/
    (Tracking)    (1 * 2)

2024/01/01 Test
    Expenses:Food    $100.00
    Assets:Cash

test reg
24-Jan-01 Test                  Expenses:Food               $100.00      $100.00
                                Assets:Cash                $-100.00            0
                                (Tracking)                  $200.00      $200.00
end test
